it.polimi.automata

Interface IBAFactory<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>

  • Type Parameters:
    STATE - is the type of the state of the Incomplete Buchi Automaton. The type of the states of the Incomplete automaton must implement the interface State
    TRANSITION - is the type of the transition of the Incomplete Buchi Automaton. The type of the transitions of the automaton must implement the interface Transition
    LABEL - is the type of the label of the transitions depending on whether the automaton represents the model or the claim it is a set of proposition or a propositional logic formula Label
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IBAFactoryImpl

    public interface IBAFactory<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>

    Represents the factory used to create an Incomplete Buchi Automaton
